panels.description: $$Input is the first stage in runner used internally for receiving messages from reader.

targets.expr: sum(increase(aio_dp_stage_incoming_messages{cluster="$cluster", cloud_resource_id="$pipeline"}[$__range]) * on(stage_id, runner_partition) group_left(stage_type, stage_name, stage_index) aio_dp_stage_info{cluster="$cluster", cloud_resource_id="$pipeline"}) by (stage_id, stage_type, stage_name, stage_index)

sum(increase(aio_dp_stage_outgoing_messages{cluster="$cluster", cloud_resource_id="$pipeline"}[$__range]) * on(stage_id, runner_partition) group_left(stage_type, stage_name, stage_index) aio_dp_stage_info{cluster="$cluster", cloud_resource_id="$pipeline"}) by (stage_id, stage_type, stage_name, stage_index)

sum(increase(aio_dp_stage_errors{cluster="$cluster", cloud_resource_id="$pipeline"}[$__range]) * on(stage_id, runner_partition) group_left(stage_type, stage_name, stage_index) aio_dp_stage_info{cluster="$cluster", cloud_resource_id="$pipeline"}) by (stage_id, stage_type, stage_name, stage_index)

avg_over_time((histogram_quantile(0.50, sum(rate(aio_dp_stage_latency_bucket{cluster="$cluster",cloud_resource_id="$pipeline"}[$__rate_interval]) * on(stage_id, runner_partition) group_left(stage_type, stage_name, stage_index) aio_dp_stage_info{cluster="$cluster", cloud_resource_id="$pipeline"}) by (le, stage_id, stage_type, stage_name, stage_index)) >= 0)[$__range:])

avg_over_time((histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(aio_dp_stage_latency_bucket{cluster="$cluster",cloud_resource_id="$pipeline"}[$__rate_interval]) * on(stage_id, runner_partition) group_left(stage_type, stage_name, stage_index) aio_dp_stage_info{cluster="$cluster", cloud_resource_id="$pipeline"}) by (le, stage_id, stage_type, stage_name, stage_index)) >= 0)[$__range:])

avg_over_time((histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(aio_dp_stage_latency_bucket{cluster="$cluster",cloud_resource_id="$pipeline"}[$__rate_interval]) * on(stage_id, runner_partition) group_left(stage_type, stage_name, stage_index) aio_dp_stage_info{cluster="$cluster", cloud_resource_id="$pipeline"}) by (le, stage_id, stage_type, stage_name, stage_index)) >= 0)[$__range:])
